{%- comment -%}
  Atlas Dependencies Section
  --------------------------
  Invisible section that loads all CSS variables, core JS/CSS files,
  and global JS variables that Atlas sections need to render correctly
  inside the host theme's theme.liquid layout.

  Must be placed FIRST in the template JSON order array.
{%- endcomment -%}

